{"type":"text","timestamp":1775879832497,"sessionID":"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm","part":{"id":"prt_d7aafc224001hs1L0KrYZVMtvP","messageID":"msg_d7aafb3bd0017U5i6r3VyFEaJ0","sessionID":"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm","type":"text","text":"Now I have all the context needed. Let me write the proposal.md for AR-031:","time":{"start":1775879832495,"end":1775879832495}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879919425,"sessionID":"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm","part":{"id":"prt_d7aafc3b2001FSyCS2QDRRMPR0","messageID":"msg_d7aafb3bd0017U5i6r3VyFEaJ0","sessionID":"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_4c30c672d5594fd0aee472be","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 RBAC 配置，将 ServiceAccount、Role/ClusterRole、RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding 从 Helm Chart 模板中独立出来，形成可单独部署的 RBAC 配置模块。该 RBAC 配置是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的权限管理基础，支撑 Workload Manager 和 Router 的访问控制需求。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **权限最小化** - 为每个组件分配精确的 RBAC 权限，遵循 least privilege 原则\n2. **模块化部署** - RBAC 配置可独立于 Helm Chart 单独部署，支持预创建权限\n3. **多租户支持** - 通过 Role/RoleBinding 支持 namespace-scoped 权限，实现多租户隔离\n4. **审计友好** - 独立的 RBAC 配置便于权限审计和安全审查\n5. **环境兼容性** - 支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化权限配置\n\n本实现基于 manifests/design.md 和 manifests/delta-spec.md 的规范，遵循 Kubernetes RBAC 最佳实践。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** manifests  \n**Language:** YAML  \n**Size:** M\n\n本 AR 包含：\n\n- **包含内容：**\n  - Workload Manager ServiceAccount 定义\n  - Workload Manager ClusterRole 定义（cluster-wide 权限）\n  - Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding 定义\n  - Router ServiceAccount 定义（可选）\n  - Router Role 定义（namespace-scoped 权限，可选）\n  - Router RoleBinding 定义（可选）\n  - RBAC 配置验证脚本\n  - 使用文档和权限说明\n\n- **不包含内容：**\n  - Helm Chart 模板（由 AR-030 管理）\n  - Kubernetes 集群配置\n  - 应用层代码修改\n  - 认证/授权逻辑实现\n\n## Current State Analysis\n\n### 现有 RBAC 配置\n\n根据 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`：\n- Workload Manager ServiceAccount 已定义\n- Workload Manager ClusterRole 已定义，包含完整的 CRD、Pods、Secrets 权限\n- Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding 已定义\n\n根据 `manifests/design.md`：\n- Router RBAC 设计为可选的 namespace-scoped Role + RoleBinding\n- Router 默认不创建 RBAC，通过 `router.rbac.create` 控制\n\n### 参考设计规范\n\n根据 `manifests/delta-spec.md` REQ-030.5 和 REQ-030.6：\n\n**Workload Manager RBAC 要求：**\n- ServiceAccount: `workloadmanager`，位于 release namespace\n- ClusterRole: `workloadmanager`，包含以下权限：\n  - `agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxes`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n  - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxclaims`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n  - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxtemplates`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n  - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n  - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools/status`: get, update, patch\n  - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n  - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/status`: get, update, patch\n  - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/finalizers`: update\n  - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes`: get, list, watch\n  - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes/status`: update, patch\n  - `pods`: get, list, watch\n  - `authentication.k8s.io/tokenreviews`: create\n  - `secrets`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n- ClusterRoleBinding: 绑定 ServiceAccount 到 ClusterRole\n\n**Router RBAC 要求：**\n- ServiceAccount: `agentcube-router`（或从 values 配置）\n- Role: namespace-scoped，包含 secrets 权限\n- RoleBinding: 绑定 ServiceAccount 到 Role\n- 可选：通过 `router.rbac.create` 控制是否创建\n\n### 差距分析\n\n1. **缺少独立 RBAC 配置** - 当前 RBAC 嵌入在 Helm Chart 中，无法单独部署\n2. **缺少权限说明文档** - 未明确说明每个权限的用途和必要性\n3. **缺少审计支持** - 无权限审计工具或检查清单\n4. **多租户支持不完整** - 缺少针对多租户场景的 Role/RoleBinding 配置\n\n### manifests/design.md 关键要求\n\n1. **权限最小化** - RBAC 权限应精确到每个资源操作\n2. **命名空间隔离** - Router RBAC 应为 namespace-scoped\n3. **可选组件支持** - Router RBAC 默认禁用，按需启用\n4. **可审计性** - RBAC 配置应易于审查和验证\n\n## Proposed Changes\n\n### 1. 目录结构\n\n```\nmanifests/rbac/\n├── README.md                       # RBAC 配置说明\n├── workloadmanager/\n│   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Workload Manager ServiceAccount\n│   ├── clusterrole.yaml            # Workload Manager ClusterRole\n│   └── clusterrolebinding.yaml     # Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding\n├── router/\n│   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Router ServiceAccount (可选)\n│   ├── role.yaml                   # Router Role (可选)\n│   └── rolebinding.yaml            # Router RoleBinding (可选)\n├── kustomization.yaml              # Kustomize 配置\n└── validate.sh                     # RBAC 验证脚本\n```\n\n### 2. Workload Manager ServiceAccount\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/rbac/workloadmanager/serviceaccount.yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  namespace: agentcube-system\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n    app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n---\n```\n\n### 3. Workload Manager ClusterRole\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/rbac/workloadmanager/clusterrole.yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRole\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n    app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\nrules:\n  # Agent Sandbox resources\n  - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  \n  # Agent Extension resources\n  - apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxclaims\", \"sandboxtemplates\", \"sandboxwarmpools\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  \n  # Warm pool status subresource\n  - apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxwarmpools/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  \n  # CodeInterpreter runtime resources\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"codeinterpreters\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n  \n  # CodeInterpreter status subresource\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"codeinterpreters/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n  \n  # CodeInterpreter finalizers\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"codeinterpreters/finalizers\"]\n    verbs: [\"update\"]\n  \n  # AgentRuntime resources (read-only)\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"agentruntimes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n  \n  # AgentRuntime status subresource\n  - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n    resources: [\"agentruntimes/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"update\", \"patch\"]\n  \n  # Pod resources (read-only for status)\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n  \n  # Token review for authentication\n  - apiGroups: [\"authentication.k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"tokenreviews\"]\n    verbs: [\"create\"]\n  \n  # Secrets for credentials and configs\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"secrets\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n```\n\n### 4. Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/rbac/workloadmanager/clusterrolebinding.yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: workloadmanager\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n    app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\nsubjects:\n  - kind: ServiceAccount\n    name: workloadmanager\n    namespace: agentcube-system\nroleRef:\n  kind: ClusterRole\n  name: workloadmanager\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n```\n\n### 5. Router ServiceAccount (Optional)\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/rbac/router/serviceaccount.yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: agentcube-router\n  namespace: agentcube-system\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n    app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n  annotations:\n    description: \"Optional - only required when router.rbac.create=true\"\n---\n```\n\n### 6. Router Role (Optional)\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/rbac/router/role.yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: Role\nmetadata:\n  name: agentcube-router\n  namespace: agentcube-system\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n    app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n  annotations:\n    description: \"Optional - namespace-scoped RBAC for Router\"\nrules:\n  # Secrets for session tokens and credentials\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"secrets\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n```\n\n### 7. Router RoleBinding (Optional)\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/rbac/router/rolebinding.yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: RoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: agentcube-router\n  namespace: agentcube-system\n  labels:\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n    app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\nsubjects:\n  - kind: ServiceAccount\n    name: agentcube-router\n    namespace: agentcube-system\nroleRef:\n  kind: Role\n  name: agentcube-router\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n```\n\n### 8. Kustomize Configuration\n\n```yaml\n# manifests/rbac/kustomization.yaml\napiVersion: kustomize.config.k8s.io/v1beta1\nkind: Kustomization\n\nnamespace: agentcube-system\n\nresources:\n  - workloadmanager/serviceaccount.yaml\n  - workloadmanager/clusterrole.yaml\n  - workloadmanager/clusterrolebinding.yaml\n  # Optional Router RBAC - uncomment to enable\n  # - router/serviceaccount.yaml\n  # - router/role.yaml\n  # - router/rolebinding.yaml\n\ncommonLabels:\n  app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube\n  app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n```\n\n### 9. RBAC 验证脚本\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# manifests/rbac/validate.sh\n\nset -e\n\nNAMESPACE=\"${NAMESPACE:-agentcube-system}\"\n\necho \"Validating RBAC configuration...\"\n\n# Check Workload Manager ServiceAccount\nif kubectl get serviceaccount workloadmanager -n \"$NAMESPACE\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n  echo \"✓ Workload Manager ServiceAccount exists\"\nelse\n  echo \"✗ Workload Manager ServiceAccount missing\"\n  exit 1\nfi\n\n# Check Workload Manager ClusterRole\nif kubectl get clusterrole workloadmanager > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n  echo \"✓ Workload Manager ClusterRole exists\"\nelse\n  echo \"✗ Workload Manager ClusterRole missing\"\n  exit 1\nfi\n\n# Check Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding\nif kubectl get clusterrolebinding workloadmanager > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n  echo \"✓ Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding exists\"\nelse\n  echo \"✗ Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding missing\"\n  exit 1\nfi\n\n# Verify ClusterRole permissions\necho \"\"\necho \"Verifying ClusterRole permissions...\"\nPERMISSIONS=$(kubectl get clusterrole workloadmanager -o jsonpath='{.rules[*].apiGroups[*]}')\nif echo \"$PERMISSIONS\" | grep -q \"agents.x-k8s.io\"; then\n  echo \"✓ agents.x-k8s.io API group present\"\nelse\n  echo \"✗ agents.x-k8s.io API group missing\"\n  exit 1\nfi\n\nif echo \"$PERMISSIONS\" | grep -q \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"; then\n  echo \"✓ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh API group present\"\nelse\n  echo \"✗ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh API group missing\"\n  exit 1\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"RBAC validation passed!\"\n```\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### 依赖影响\n\n| 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| Kubernetes | ≥1.21 | RBAC API |\n| kubectl | ≥1.21 | 部署和验证 |\n| Kustomize | ≥4.0 | 配置管理 |\n\n### 模块依赖关系\n\n```\nmanifests/rbac/\n├── workloadmanager/\n│   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # 无依赖\n│   ├── clusterrole.yaml            # 依赖 CRD 定义 (AR-017)\n│   └── clusterrolebinding.yaml     # 依赖 ServiceAccount + ClusterRole\n├── router/\n│   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # 无依赖\n│   ├── role.yaml                   # 无依赖\n│   └── rolebinding.yaml            # 依赖 ServiceAccount + Role\n├── kustomization.yaml              # 依赖所有 RBAC 文件\n└── validate.sh                     # 依赖 kubectl\n```\n\n### 向后兼容性\n\n- 首次实现，无破坏性变更风险\n- 与 AR-030 Helm Chart 中的 RBAC 配置兼容（内容一致，组织形式不同）\n- 支持独立部署或与 Helm Chart 协同部署\n\n### 测试影响\n\n- 需要验证 RBAC 权限的正确性（`kubectl auth can-i`）\n- 需要验证命名空间隔离（Router Role 应为 namespace-scoped）\n- 需要验证 ServiceAccount 与 Role/ClusterRole 的绑定关系\n\n### 与 AR-030 的关系\n\nAR-030 的 Helm Chart 中包含的 RBAC 模板与本 AR 的独立 RBAC 配置内容一致，但使用场景不同：\n\n| 场景 | AR-030 (Helm) | AR-031 (独立) |\n|------|---------------|---------------|\n| 快速部署 | ✓ | ✗ |\n| 预创建权限 | ✗ | ✓ |\n| 权限审计 | ✗ | ✓ |\n| 多租户配置 | ✗ | ✓ |\n| 环境隔离 | 通过 values | 通过 kustomize |\n\n推荐流程：先使用 AR-031 预创建 RBAC，再使用 AR-030 Helm Chart 部署应用。\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### 方案 1: 仅使用 Helm Chart RBAC（不独立）\n\n**优点:**\n- 简单，单一部署单元\n- 无需额外工具\n\n**缺点:**\n- 无法预创建权限\n- 权限审计困难\n- 与 Helm release 绑定，难以跨环境复用\n\n**决策:** 提供独立 RBAC 配置，支持与 Helm 解耦部署。\n\n### 方案 2: 使用 RBAC Management Operator\n\n**优点:**\n- 自动化 RBAC 生命周期管理\n- 支持动态权限调整\n\n**缺点:**\n- 增加运维复杂度\n- 需要额外的 Operator 部署\n\n**决策:** 采用静态 YAML 配置，保持简单可控。\n\n### 方案 3: 单一巨型 RBAC 文件\n\n**优点:**\n- 文件数量少\n- 易于复制\n\n**缺点:**\n- 难以维护\n- 不支持按需启用组件\n\n**决策:** 采用模块化组织（每个组件独立目录），提高可维护性。\n\n### 方案 4: ClusterRole vs Role 选择\n\n**Workload Manager:** 选择 ClusterRole，因为需要：\n- 访问跨 namespace 的 CRD\n- 管理多个租户的 Sandbox\n\n**Router:** 选择 Role，因为：\n- 仅需访问本 namespace 的 Secrets\n- 支持多租户隔离\n\n**决策:** 根据组件需求选择合适的 RBAC 作用域。\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### 权限验证\n\n1. **Workload Manager 权限验证**\n   ```bash\n   kubectl auth can-i create sandboxes --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube-system:workloadmanager\n   kubectl auth can-i get codeinterpreters --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube-system:workloadmanager\n   kubectl auth can-i update secrets --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube-system:workloadmanager\n   ```\n\n2. **Router 权限验证**\n   ```bash\n   kubectl auth can-i get secrets -n agentcube-system --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube-system:agentcube-router\n   ```\n\n### 隔离验证\n\n1. **命名空间隔离** - 验证 Router Role 无法访问其他 namespace\n2. **权限最小化** - 验证 RBAC 仅包含必需权限\n\n### 集成测试\n\n1. **Kind 集群测试** - 在 Kind 集群上实际安装验证\n2. **应用联调** - 验证 Workload Manager 和 Router 能正常使用分配的权限\n\n### 测试覆盖目标\n\n- ServiceAccount: 100%（所有组件）\n- ClusterRole/Role: 100%（所有权限规则）\n- Binding: 100%（所有绑定关系）\n- 验证脚本: 100%（所有检查项）\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Workload Manager ServiceAccount 可创建\n- [ ] Workload Manager ClusterRole 权限完整\n- [ ] Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding 正确绑定\n- [ ] Router ServiceAccount 可创建（可选）\n- [ ] Router Role 权限正确（可选）\n- [ ] Router RoleBinding 正确绑定（可选）\n- [ ] `kubectl apply -k` 成功\n- [ ] 验证脚本通过所有检查\n- [ ] 权限验证通过（`kubectl auth can-i`）\n- [ ] 文档完整（权限说明、使用示例）\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### 必需依赖\n- Kubernetes ≥1.21（RBAC API）\n- kubectl ≥1.21\n- Kustomize ≥4.0\n\n### 被依赖\n- AR-017 (CRD 定义) - ClusterRole 权限依赖 CRD\n- AR-030 (Helm Chart) - 可选协同部署\n\n## Migration Notes\n\n### 从 Helm Chart RBAC 迁移\n\n1. 备份现有 RBAC 配置\n   ```bash\n   kubectl get serviceaccount,clusterrole,clusterrolebinding -l app.kubernetes.io/name=workloadmanager -o yaml > backup.yaml\n   ```\n\n2. 应用独立 RBAC 配置\n   ```bash\n   kubectl apply -k manifests/rbac/\n   ```\n\n3. 验证权限\n   ```bash\n   ./manifests/rbac/validate.sh\n   ```\n\n4. 更新 Helm Chart（可选）\n   - 禁用 Helm Chart 中的 RBAC 创建\n   - 或保留 Helm Chart RBAC（内容一致，无冲突）\n\n### 破坏性变更\n无 - 首次实现。\n\n### 行为变更\n- RBAC 配置从 Helm Chart 中解耦\n- 支持独立部署和版本控制\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. 是否需要支持自定义命名空间？（通过 kustomize namespace 字段）\n2. 是否需要提供 RBAC 审计日志？（待需求明确）\n3. 是否需要支持动态权限更新？（待需求明确）\n\n## References\n\n- `manifests/design.md` - Manifests 设计文档\n- `manifests/delta-spec.md` - Manifests 规范（REQ-030.5, REQ-030.6）\n- `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` - 现有 Helm RBAC 模板\n- Kubernetes RBAC Best Practices: https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/access-authn-authz/rbac/\n- Kustomize Documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/manage-kubernetes-objects/kustomization/\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775879919407,"end":1775879919421}}}}
